{1:top LambdaStreamsPromise}

Javascript promise helpers for {{:https://github.com/Risto-Stevcev/lambda-streams}lambda-streams}.

{2 Usage}

{ul
{- {!Promise.first_to_promise} converts the {i first} signal of a finite async stream into a promise.}
{- {!Promise.last_to_promise} converts the {i last} signal of a finite async stream into a promise.}
{- {!Promise.from_promise} converts a promise into a finite async stream.}
}

See {!Promise} for more info.
